1) Clone the project using the command : git clone https://github.com/Prajwal-2304/TextClassifier.git
2) Navigate to the cloned folder and create a virtual environment using python -m venv venv 
3) Activate the environement using .\venv\Scripts\activate
4)Install Flask dependencies using pip install -r requirements.txt
5)Start the Flask backend using python app.py 
6)Navigate to text-classifier folder and install the dependencies using npm install 
7)Start the React frontend using npm start 


